text: Tenshi No Gijinka is an album by Japanese musician Keiji Haino, released on John Zorn's Tzadik label in 1995. The album features nine untitled pieces, consisting of Haino's voice and percussion. ==Track listing== ==External links== * Category:1995 albums Category:Keiji Haino albums Category:Tzadik Records albums
title: Tenshi No Gijinka
